overview: Artist Fia-Stina Sandlund and actor Alexandra Dahlstroem are to give a performance at the Venice Biennale. Dahlstroem, in character as Julie, will answer questions about Sandlund's upcoming feature, a feminist reinterpretation of the famous August Strindberg play Miss Julie. This is Dahsltroem's audition.
title: She's Blonde Like Me
